title: Good, for the first Android build of Freeminer.
comment: I usually play Minetest (What Freeminer originally got forked from.) This build is made well. All GUIs fit in the screen. Shame it can only connect to a limited amount of servers..... I tried connecting to one, and when it got halfway through Media, it restarted..... Seems I have insufficient RAM. Anyways, that's an improvement compared to MT Android builds. It just crashes all other apps, trying to get memory. I like the slippery ice, yet the movement keys are a little too small for my liking.
